notes "Here endeth the first argument. Increment the local variable Osw_Euth_Arg_1 by 1.\nAlthough it's not a pro-euthanasia arguement per se, by defining what he wants and setting some clear limits, Dr. Oswald is reassuring the PC that the practice is much less likely to be abused."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Naturally, the practice needs to be very tightly regulated. I would never administer euthanasia to anyone who was not conscious and lucid enough to reliably make the decision to end their own lives for themselves."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Go on." linkto "Osw_6_05a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "That's not an argument in favor of legalizing it, though." linkto "Osw_6_05b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about something else instead." linkto "Osw_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Maybe we should talk about this another time. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
