Node "Osw_6_08_1"
notes "Here endeth the second argument. Increment the local variable Osw_Euth_Arg_2 by 1.\nOswald has illustrated the lack of resources and medical staffing in Sandover."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "My point is that, if a patient doesn't stand a cockroach's chance in hell of survival, we should concentrate resources that would be used on them to help other poor souls who probably would survive. Sandover is no place for the sick to hang around waiting, either."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I see your point." linkto "Osw_6_09"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "That's a callous way of dealing with your patients - it means you're basically choosing who lives and who dies." linkto "Osw_6_08_2b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Why is Sandover a bad place for ill people to wait for treatment?" linkto "Osw_6_08_2a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about something else instead." linkto "Osw_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Maybe we should talk about this another time. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Osw_6_08_2a_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Haven't you heard that Sandover has a higher level of background radiation than the rest of the wastes?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Actually, yes." linkto "Osw_6_08_2a_2a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "No, has it?" linkto "Osw_6_08_2a_2b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about something else instead." linkto "Osw_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Maybe we should talk about this another time. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Osw_6_08_2a_2a"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Then you shouldn't need to ask why it's a bad place for the sick to be waiting for treatment."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I guess not." linkto "Osw_6_09"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about something else instead." linkto "Osw_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Maybe we should talk about this another time. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Osw_6_08_2a_2b"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Yes, it has. You needn't worry if you're not planning on any length of time here. It only affects those of us who live here for years. But you can see why Sandover is no place for the ill to be forced to wait for treatment."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I see your point." linkto "Osw_6_09"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about something else instead." linkto "Osw_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Maybe we should talk about this another time. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Osw_6_08_2b"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "No-one's pretending it isn't callous. But that's life in the wastes for you, stranger. A man in my position is forced to make those kinds of decisions on a daily basis."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I see your point." linkto "Osw_6_09"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Why is Sandover a bad place for ill people to wait for treatment?" linkto "Osw_6_08_2a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about something else instead." linkto "Osw_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Maybe we should talk about this another time. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Osw_6_09"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Something else to consider is that of the patients coming into my hospital, a much greater proportion have illnesses that are radiation-related and terminal than you'd find in hospitals in other towns in the wastes."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Go on." linkto "Osw_6_10"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I see, but I don't understand how that's relevant." linkto "Osw_6_10"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about something else instead." linkto "Osw_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Maybe we should talk about this another time. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Osw_6_10"
notes "Here endeth the third argument. Increment the local variable Osw_Euth_Arg_3 by 1.\nDr. Oswald has pointed out the higher percentage of terminal cases that come into his hospital."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "That means that I have to offer a higher number of beds and resources per capita to patients who aren't going to make it. Sandover is the last place on earth which can afford that sort of... indulgence, when you consider how badly our resources are stretched in the first place."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "So the need for euthanasia is more pressing in Sandover than anywhere else." linkto "Osw_6_11a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "'Indulgence'? I hardly think making life easier for terminal patients is pampering them." linkto "Osw_6_11b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about something else instead." linkto "Osw_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Maybe we should talk about this another time. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Osw_6_11a"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Precisely. Well put."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Go on." linkto "Osw_6_12"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about something else instead." linkto "Osw_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Maybe we should talk about this another time. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Osw_6_11b"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "You misunderstand me. When I used the word 'indulgence', I'm talking about the difference between accepting the hard realities of our over-stretched healthcare system and what we might wish for in better circumstances."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "So you're saying the need for euthanasia is more pressing in Sandover than anywhere else." linkto "Osw_6_11a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about something else instead." linkto "Osw_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Maybe we should talk about this another time. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Osw_6_12"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "And that brings me on to my next point. Putting aside the patients who have no chance of survival a moment. What about their relatives?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What about them?" linkto "Osw_6_13a_1"  notes "If the PC has cured Fran, go to Osw_6_13b_1 instead. If the PC has convinced Dr. Oswald to euthanase Fran, go to Osw_6_13c_1 instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about something else instead." linkto "Osw_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Maybe we should talk about this another time. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Osw_6_13a_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Take one of my current patients for example. Fran, her name is. I'm almost certain she isn't going to see this year out. That's bad enough, except she has a son, Connor, here in Sandover, too."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[MORE]" linkto "Osw_6_13a_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about something else instead." linkto "Osw_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Maybe we should talk about this another time. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Osw_6_13a_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Let's assume that the only thing keeping both Connor and his mother in Sandover is Fran's illness. Heaven forbid, but if Fran were to die tomorrow, there would be nothing tying Connor to Sandover and he could leave whenever he wished."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[MORE]" linkto "Osw_6_14"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about something else instead." linkto "Osw_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Maybe we should talk about this another time. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Osw_6_13b_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "If a patient has relatives in Sandover, not only does the patient suffer exposure to Sandover's higher levels of radiation, whether they're receiving treatment or not - their relatives do, too"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[MORE]" linkto "Osw_6_13b_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about something else instead." linkto "Osw_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Maybe we should talk about this another time. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
