Node "Osw_7_1c_1"
notes "The Osw_7_1c_* path is used when the PC wants to talk to Dr. Oswald about the diagnosis he made on Fran."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Yes, she's suffering terribly, the poor woman. What did you have in mind?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "All her symptoms indicate massive radiation poisoning. We should treat her with anti-rad drugs at once." linkto "Osw_7_1c_2a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I don't think she stands much chance of survival. She'd be better off dead than alive." linkto "Osw_7_1c_2b_1"  notes "If the PC has completed the 'Resolve the euthanasia debate' quest and persuaded Alexander to ban euthanasia, go to Osw_7_1c_2c_1 instead."
              }
