}
Node "Osw_7_1c_2a_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "[Oswald nods in solemn agreement.] Yes, that sounds about right. It's a massive dose, though. [He smiles ruefully.] You can appreciate my position, Doctor <PC> - that represents nearly a month's worth of anti-rad drugs for all of Sandover!"
      options {
