 NPCFemaleText "[Oswald fixes you with a steely glare.] Come on, Doctor. You're a medical woman. You're aware of what the harsh realities of a hospital force us to do. Yes, I'm talking about giving her, you know, the final mercy."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[MORE]" linkto "Osw_7_1c_2a_3a_3"  notes ""
