Node "Osw_7_1c_2b_3b_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Be that as it may, given that our diagnoses concur, I am convinced it's the best course of action. If she's lucid enough and agrees to it, I will give Fran a lethal dose of drugs. Don't worry, Doctor; she won't feel a thing."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "If you take one step towards that woman, I'll strike you down where you stand." linkto "Osw_7_1c_2b_3b_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Is this even legal in Sandover?" linkto "Osw_6_01"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "In that case, do what you have to do. I wash my hands of it." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Osw_7_1c_2b_3b_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Then strike, Doctor. My diagnosis will not be altered by intimidation."
      options {
