          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Have it your way. [Draw weapon.]" linkto "combat"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Osw_7_1c_2c_1"
notes "The Osw_7_1c_2c_* path is used when the PC suggests that Fran would be better off dead, but Dr. Oswald cannot euthanase her because the PC persuaded Alexander to ban the practice."
