notes "Increment the local variable Osw_Hosp_Attempt by 1."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Hmm. It sounds to me like you've got a reasonable grounding in basic first aid, but you've a long way to go if you ever want to practice as a doctor. Thank you for the offer, but you aren't ready to work with my patients."
      options {
