Node "Osw_8_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Why do I seem busy? In case you hadn't noticed, I work in a hospital. You'll find doctors are usually kept on their toes. Mind you, I have a mountain of other problems on top of that to make matters worse."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What problems are those?" linkto "Osw_8_2"  notes "If the PC has fixed the Autodoc AND NOT completed the 'Challenge the Tech Supplies caravan's charges' quest in such a way that the caravan's prices are lowered, go to Osw_8_3 instead.\nIf the PC has fixed the Autodoc AND completed the 'Challenge the Tech Supplies caravan's charges' quest in such a way that the caravan's prices are lowered AND NOT completed the 'Resolve the euthanasia debate' quest, go to Osw_8_4_1 instead.\nIf the PC has fixed the Autodoc AND completed the 'Challenge the Tech Supplies caravan's charges' quest in such a way that the caravan's prices are lowered AND completed the 'Resolve the euthanasia debate' quest, go to Osw_8_5 instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sore subject. Let me ask you about something else." linkto "Osw_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sorry to hear that. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Osw_8_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Take my Autodoc, for instance. The damn thing refuses to work. Without it, I'm forced to spend hours on routine operations that used to take five minutes."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me have a look. I'm quite skilled at mechanical repairs." linkto "Osw_3_1a_1"  notes "This node only appears if the PC has not already fixed the Autodoc."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Is that the only thing that is causing you problems?" linkto "Osw_8_3"  notes "If the PC has completed the 'Challenge the Tech Supplies caravan's charges' quest in such a way that the caravan's prices are lowered AND NOT completed the 'Resolve the euthanasia debate' quest, go to Osw_8_4_1 instead.\nIf the PC has completed the 'Challenge the Tech Supplies caravan's charges' quest in such a way that the caravan's prices are lowered AND completed the 'Resolve the euthanasia debate' quest, go to Osw_8_5 instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sore subject. Let me ask you about something else." linkto "Osw_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sorry to hear that. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Osw_8_3"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I'm short on day-to-day day medical supplies, too. Meds, stims, anti-rads, you name it. I have to stretch the doses I give out so thinly they're practically a waste of time."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What's causing this shortage of supplies?" linkto "Osw_5a_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Do you have any other set-backs?" linkto "Osw_8_4_1"  notes "If the PC has completed the 'Resolve the euthanasia debate' quest, go to Osw_8_5 instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sore subject. Let me ask you about something else." linkto "Osw_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sorry to hear that. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Osw_8_4_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "There are certain people in Sandover who are standing in the way of more... progressive medical thinking. These people mean well, but their archaic viewpoints are directly holding me back."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What is it they're complaining about?" linkto "Osw_8_4_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "'Progressive medical thinking'? Not sure I like the sound of that." linkto "Osw_8_4_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sore subject. Let me ask you about something else." linkto "Osw_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sorry to hear that. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Osw_8_4_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I'm talking about the discussion that has raged in Sandover for years about euthanasia. It would mean a great deal to this town if we allowed its very ill citizens to choose when they wanted to die."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Could you tell me a bit more about your views regarding euthanasia?" linkto "Osw_6_02"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Which people in Sandover are against euthanasia?" linkto "Osw_8_4_3"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about something else." linkto "Osw_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Doesn't sound very progressive to me. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Osw_8_4_3"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "There are several people who have Alexander, our leader's, ear who don't support the legalization of euthanasia, and who stand in the way of the process's legitimization. David, Michael's acolyte is amongst the most vocal."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Could you tell me a bit more about your views regarding euthanasia?" linkto "Osw_6_02"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Where can I find David?" linkto "Osw_8_4_4"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sore subject. Let me ask you about something else." linkto "Osw_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sorry to hear that. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
